

## 这是 https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models 的代理
POST https://gemini.829525.xyz/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "models/gemini-2.5-flash",
  "input": {
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "input_text",
        "text": "What is Gemini?"
      }
    ]
  }
}


curl -v -X POST https://gemini.829525.xyz/v1beta/models \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"model":"models/gemini-2.5-flash","input":{"content":[{"type":"input_text","text":"Hello"}]}}'